name: 格伦·安德烈·维斯特·博伊
name_full: 格伦·安德烈·维斯特·博伊 Glenn André Viste Bøe

last_movies.title: Buzz Aldrin, hvor ble det av deg i alt mylderet?

introduction: Glenn Andre Viste Bøe was born in Stavanger in 1992. During his childhood he has always loved to perform on stage. Starting lower secondary school, he joined the Child and Youth Theatre at Rogaland Teater. Acting the role of "Alexander" in the short film "Sting" (2007) was his first experience with the film industry. Coming to Norwegian cinemas in March 2012, he is playing the role of "Helge Ombo" in the award winning "Company Orheim", the third and last film about "Jarle Klepp".
